Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是很难被找到嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披萨以及..这是沙拉碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙拉？附赠的么 我又不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了多少天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几天如此平淡无事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会被找到了吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微..出去透透气吧
